notes.note: The easiest way to get icons on your website is with a Kit. It's your very own custom version of Font Awesome, all bundled up with only the icons, tools, and settings you need.
No matter matter what tech you're using for your project, website, or app, we have the tools that work how and where you do.
Font Awesome is the internet's icon library and toolkit used by millions of designers, developers, and content creators.
